Connectivity
============

There are many connectivity options available on the |product| industrial PC. It has |USB|; |LAN|; up to |uart_at_most|, up to |can_at_most|.

RS232/RS485/CAN
---------------

The serial communication interfaces (RS485, RS232, and CAN) are routed to a |conn_terminal|, as illustrated on the figure below.

.. rst-class:: text-center

  |rs232_485_can_img|

  *RS232, RS485 and CAN*

|UART_Note|




